ow up](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=577.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Monitor GSC data issues and re-evaluate next week for more accurate insights](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=420.0)\n  - [Investigate expense category page traffic drop if trend continues](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=318.0)\n  - [Victoria to update status for next batch of vendor pages](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=480.0)\n  - [growthx.ai to deliver bank fact articles by Monday](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=496.0)\n  - Ali to provide list of blogs for refresh\n  - [Vivek to follow up on cannibalization check workflows](https://fathom.video/share/swYyTqCRapy7pJsBzy4yL6KbJ6Yicwxz?tab=summary&timestamp=577.0)\n"
